Privacy Policy

Thank you for choosing to use Space Basketball Challenge. This privacy policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our app.

Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information from our users.

When you use Space Basketball Challenge, we do collect non-personal information such as your device type, operating system version, and app usage data. This information is used to help us understand how users interact with our app and to make improvements to the user experience.

How We Use Your Information

The non-personal information we collect is used solely for the purpose of improving the app and providing a better user experience. We do not share, sell, or rent any information collected through the app with third parties.

We do not use cookies or any other tracking technologies.

Data Security

We take data security seriously and have implemented appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction of the information we collect.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update or modify this privacy policy at any time. You are encouraged to review this policy periodically to ensure that you are aware of any changes.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please do not hesitate to contact us at [insert your contact email address].

